Retrieve COVID-19 data for counties in a state(s)

Source: R/getAdmn2ByState.R
getAdmn2ByState.Rd

Retrieve up-to-date COVID-19 data from outbreak.info for all counties in one or more states/provinces.

getAdmn2ByState(states, ...)

Arguments

states:

vector or list of state name(s)

Value

dataframe

Examples

getAdmn2ByState("California")
